quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  16,94,"Wata on jogitor goondooje mon ﾉ容n janfondiro hakkunde mon, jokkiron ﾉ蓉m mbeleeﾉ容 mon, firtiron ﾉ容 no faaliraﾉ熔n, hunnon ko faalaﾉ熔n e majje. Anndee si on waﾉ擁i ﾉ蓉m, koyﾉ容 mon ﾉ容n mortoto e laawol focciingol ngol ﾉ殿awo nde ﾉ容 tabitunoo e maggol, kadi, on meeﾉ擁ray lepte ﾉ容n sabu majjugol mon e laawol Alla ngol majjinorﾉ熔n woﾉ遼兎 goo. Hino woodani on lepte cowanlle."
  16,95,"Wata on waﾉ葉itir ahadi Alla ndin jawkal fanﾉ蓉ngel e firtugol ndi ronka hunnude ndi. Anndee ko ko woni ka Alla kon immorde e ballal, e teetateeri aduna, e ko woni ka Makko laakara kon immorde e neemaa- ji duumotooﾉ擁, ko ﾉ蓉m ﾉ砥ri moﾆｴﾆｴande on e dii ko waﾉ葉irton e coggu fanﾉ蓉ngu fii firtugol ahadi, si tawno hiﾉ熔n anndi ﾉ蓉m!"
  16,96,"Ko marﾉ熔n kon onon ﾉ兎e yimﾉ兎, immorde e jawle e wellitaare, e neemaaji fow ko ko lannata, ko ﾉ擁 ﾉ蓉uﾉ擁 woo non. Ko woni Alla kon kan e mbarjaari, ko ko heddoto. Ko honno ﾉ砥rnirton ko lannata e hoore ko heddotoo? Ma Men warjor ﾉ兎n muﾃｱﾃｱiiﾉ兎 e hunnugol ahadiiji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n ﾉ兎 salii firtugol ﾉ擁 mbarjaari maﾉ橡兎 ndin, ko ﾉ砥ri moﾆｴﾆｴude e ko ﾉ兎 gollaaynoo e dewe. Men yoﾉ妬tira ﾉ兎 moﾆｴﾆｴere kala sappo yeru mayre, haa teemeﾉ遼容 jeeﾉ擁ﾉ擁, haa ﾉ砥ra ﾉ蓉mn cowe ﾉ蓉uﾉ擁."
  16,97,"Kala golluﾉ熔 gollal moﾆｴﾆｴal, harondiral e sar'ia, woni gorko maa debbo, hara ko o gomﾉ擁nﾉ熔 Alla, Ma Men wuurno mo aduna, nguurndam laaﾉ砥ﾉ預m, wonndude e weltorgol ﾃｱaawoore Alla nden, e yonndinaare, e hawrindineede e peewal. Ma Men yoﾉ妬tiroy ﾉ兎 kadi njoﾉ電i maﾉ橡兎 ndin laakara, ko ﾉ砥ri moﾆｴﾆｴude e kon ko ﾉ兎 gollaynoo aduna e golle moﾆｴﾆｴe."
  16,98,"An oo gomﾉ擁nﾉ熔, si a faandike janngugol Alqur'aana, toro Alla nde moolat maa e sowonsi seytaane raﾉ預aﾉ熔 e yurmeende Alla nden."
  16,99,"Kanko seytaane, mbawdi alanaa mo e ﾉ兎n gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 Alla, ﾉ兎 fawi denndaangal fiyaakuuji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n e hoore Joomi maﾉ橡兎 tun."
  16,100,"Anndee mbawdi makko ndin ko sowonsingol ﾉ兎n welduﾉ兎 e makko ﾉ兎 ﾉ熔ftii mo e bewre, e ﾉ兎n sirkiranooﾉ兎 Alla sabu ko o e bewre makko nden."
  16,101,"Si Men lontinirii ﾃｱaawoore Aaye Alqur'aana lonto Aaya goo - Ko Alla ﾉ砥ri anndude ko O lontinta kon ka Alqur'aana ﾃｱenﾆｴal Makko, annduﾉ熔 ko O lontintaa e mayre kon - ﾆ‘ wi'a ontuma: An Muhammadu, ko a fenoowo baka e Alla. Si ko woni, ko ﾉ砥ri ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉de e maﾉ橡兎 anndaa wonnde lontingol ngol, ko ﾃｱaawooree Alla yottoriinde ﾃｱenﾆｴal Makko."
  16,102,"Maakan ﾉ兎 an Nulaaﾉ熔: Ko jippini O Alquraana ko jibriilu (yo o his), immorde ka Alla seniiﾉ熔 On, e hoore goonga mo faljere alaa e mu'un nde waylaa- ka nde waﾉ葉itaaka. ﾆ隔m, ko fii no o tabintinira giomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 Alla ﾉ兎n e gomﾉ擁nal maﾉ橡兎 ngal tuma kala nde kesum jippii e mayre, goﾉ遼蓉m kadi lontinaa, kadi, ko fii no nde wonira feewirde maﾉ橡兎 e goonga, e welo-welo wonannde juulﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, sabu ko nde heﾉ登rta kon mbarjaari teddundi."